Ant: Distributed mitigation actions, community adaptation
Crow: Tipping point prediction, transformation pathway design
```

Case Study: Arctic Ice Preservation

· Stallion: Emergency albedo enhancement deployment
· Ant: Distributed methane monitoring network
· Crow: Prediction of ice-free Arctic timelines and cascading effects
· Result: 15-year extension of summer ice cover, preventing catastrophic feedback loops

4.4 Enterprise Digital Transformation

